cai ham read_file la
  given a path of text, returns the file contents as text.
  can the path is within the allowed workspace root.
  bao_dam the contents reflect the file at the time of the read.

cai ham write_file la
  given a path of text and contents of text, returns yes or no.
  can the path is within the allowed workspace root.
  can the contents are valid utf-8 text.
  bao_dam the file at the path matches the contents after the call returns yes.

cai ham list_dir la
  given a path of text, returns a list of file names as text.
  can the path is a directory within the allowed workspace root.
  bao_dam the listing excludes hidden files unless explicitly requested.
